Privacy Policy
Last updated: Aug 31, 2024 12:30 AM
Introduction
Welcome to Trend App. Trend App (“us”, “we”, or “our”) operates Trend (hereinafter referred to as “Service”)
Our Privacy Policy governs your visit to Trend application, and explains how we collect, safeguard and disclose information that results from your use of our Service
We use your data to provide and improve Service. By using Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. Unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy, the terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions. .
Our Terms and Conditions (“Terms”) govern all use of our Service and together with the Privacy Policy constitutes your agreement with us (“agreement”).
User Registration and Accounts
Account Creation Procedures
To access certain features of our mobile application, users are required to create an account. We offer multiple options for account creation to suit your preferences and convenience:
Email Registration:
You can create an account using your email address. Simply provide a valid email, set a password, and follow the prompts to complete your registration.
Apple Login::
You may choose to create an account or log in using your Apple ID. This option allows you to use your Apple credentials to access our application securely.
Google Login:
You can also sign up or log in using your Google account. This option simplifies the registration process by utilizing your existing Google account information.
Facebook Login:
We offer the ability to create an account or log in using your Facebook credentials, enabling quick and easy access to our application.
Instagram Login:
Users have the option to sign up or log in using their Instagram account, providing another convenient way to access our application.
User Responsibilities
By creating an account, you agree to the following responsibilities:
Account Security:
You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials, including your username and password. Do not share your credentials with others. If you suspect any unauthorized use of your account, you must notify us immediately.
Accurate Information:
Ensure that all information provided during registration is accurate and up-to-date. Inaccurate or outdated information may affect your access to the application and our ability to provide services to you.
Compliance with Terms:
You must comply with all terms and conditions outlined in this Privacy Policy and our Terms of Service. Any breach of these terms may result in the suspension or termination of your account.
We are committed to safeguarding your personal information and ensuring the security of our services. If you have any questions or concerns about your account, please contact our support team for assistance on
support@trend.app
