To provide an enhanced user experience, our mobile application requires access to your location. You will be prompted to grant permission for the app to access your location data. You can manage and change these permissions at any time through your device’s settings.
Use of Location Data
We utilize location data to improve the functionality and efficiency of our services. Specifically, your location information is used for the following purposes:
Delivery Services:
Accurate location data ensures that delivery services are optimized, providing precise and timely deliveries to your specified address.
Address Verification:
By accessing your location, we can verify and enhance the accuracy of addresses entered in the app, reducing errors and ensuring correct deliveries.
Google Login:
You can also sign up or log in using your Google account. This option simplifies the registration process by utilizing your existing Google account information
Facebook Login:
